---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="CV — Bruno Mentges"
  description="How to get a detailed CV with references and company names. Summary version with anonymized highlights is on this page."
>
  <article class="cv">
    <div class="container-prose">
      <header class="cv-hero">
        <span class="section-label">CV</span>
        <h1>Curriculum Vitae</h1>
        <p class="lede">
          A detailed CV with company names and references is available by request
          or on LinkedIn. This page is a summary of the shape of my experience.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="prose cv-body">
        <h2>Get the full CV</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/brunomentgesdecarvalho/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn profile</a>
            {' '}— detailed roles, dates, and recommendations
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/bmentges" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
            {' '}— code, open source, projects
          </li>
          <li>
            Email — reach out via LinkedIn for a tailored copy (EN or PT-BR) in PDF
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Summary</h2>
        <p>
          Senior Data Engineer &amp; AI Engineer with ~25 years of software engineering and
          ~15 years specialized in data platforms. Currently focused on integrating LLM agents
          into production data workflows. Native Portuguese, fluent English (C2). Based in
          Rio de Janeiro, available for remote international engagements or relocation with
          visa sponsorship.
        </p>

        <h2>Highlights</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Petabyte-scale ad data</strong> — 1.5B records/day on AWS EMR/Hadoop, powering real-time ad optimization for thousands of advertisers.</li>
          <li><strong>Self-healing finance pipeline</strong> — replaced a recurring monthly manual data-repair cycle with automated detect-and-remediate, running unattended at close.</li>
          <li><strong>Data platform from zero</strong> — stood up a full Google Cloud data platform (lake, warehouse, analytics) for a logistics company adopting data-as-a-product.</li>
          <li><strong>Production AI integration</strong> — shipped Anthropic Claude agents with guardrails, skills, and tool-use into day-to-day data engineering; extended with Model Context Protocol (MCP).</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Core stack</h2>
        <p>
          Python, SQL, Scala, Java, TypeScript. Snowflake, BigQuery, Redshift. dbt, Airflow,
          Prefect. Spark, Hadoop. AWS (primary), GCP, Azure. Terraform, Docker, Kubernetes.
          Anthropic Claude (primary LLM), MCP, self-hosted models.
        </p>

        <h2>Education</h2>
        <p>
          Bachelor of Technology — Computer Science (Centro Universitário Carioca, 2006–2011).
        </p>

        <h2>Languages</h2>
        <p>
          English (fluent, C2) · Portuguese (native).
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .cv {
    padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
  }
  .cv-hero {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  .cv-hero h1 {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }
  .cv-hero .lede {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 55ch;
  }
  .cv-body h2 {
    margin-top: 2.75rem;
  }
</style>
